# Summary
This documentation details the Azure Blob Storage destination in Amplitude, which enables exporting event data and merged user data to Azure containers with hourly recurring syncs, including the required Azure prerequisites (service principal setup, permissions), configuration steps, manual export process, and the exported data formats for both events and merged Amplitude IDs.

